Name: Hentai Pix
About the game: 'Hentai Pix' is a fantastic game, You can add any favorite pictures to the game, support jpg, png format, Can touch and graffiti, Make the picture look more sexy ! Game features -Dynamic picture Games can make pictures dynamic, Make the picture look more sexy ! -Powerful graffiti function You can add something to the picture! -Custom picture You can add any favorite pictures to the game -Adjust touch Setting interface can adjust touch range R, touch intensity S, touch elasticity E -Automatic touch Right mouse button is automatic mode, Can let you free your hands to do other things -Jigsaw game The game contains a variety of jigsaw puzzles that can be selected through the game settings
